'''哈伍德宮'''（{{lang-en|Harewood House}}、{{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|ɑ:r|w|ʊ|d}}、{{respell|HAR|wuud}}、{{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|ɛər|-}}、{{respell|HAIR|-}}）<ref>{{cite news |last1=Lyall |first1=Sarah |title=Great Brington Journal; Why Can't the English . . . ? It's Pronounced Clahss |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/05/31/world/great-brington-journal-why-can-t-the-english-it-s-pronounced-clahss.html |access-date=2018-09-28 |work=The New York Times |date=2000-03-31 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103624/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/05/31/world/great-brington-journal-why-can-t-the-english-it-s-pronounced-clahss.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>是一座位於[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[西約克郡|西約克郡]][[哈伍德|哈伍德]]的[[英格蘭鄉村別墅|英格蘭鄉村別墅]]。這座建築由{{link-en|約翰·卡爾|John Carr (architect)}}和[[羅伯特·亞當|羅伯特·亞當]]設計，修建於1759年至1771年，最初的所有者是{{link-en|愛德溫·拉塞爾斯, 第一代哈伍德男爵|Edwin Lascelles, 1st Baron Harewood|愛德溫·拉塞爾斯}}，一位富裕的[[西印度群島|西印度群島]]種植園主和奴隸主。景觀設計者是[[萬能的布朗|萬能的布朗]]，面積達{{convert|1000|acre}}。

拉塞爾斯家族現仍居住在這裡。哈伍德宮是{{link-en|英格蘭珍貴莊園|Treasure Houses of England}}的成員之一，也是I級[[登錄建築|登錄建築]]。

==歷史==
===早期歷史===
哈伍德宮是由兩個相鄰的莊園合併而成，分別是基於{{link-en|哈伍德城堡|Harewood Castle}}修建的哈伍德莊園，以及基於高索普別墅修建的高索普莊園（Gawthorpe estate）。高索普家族購買了哈伍德莊園，將兩者合併。1696年，莊園被售給倫敦商人{{link-en|約翰·卡特勒|Sir John Cutler, 1st Baronet}}。此後又售給布特勒（Boulter）家族。1721年，布特勒家族將其售給拉塞爾斯<ref>{{cite book|title=The Civil, Ecclesiastical, Literary, Commercial, and Miscellaneous of Leeds etc|volume=1|page=215}}</ref>。
===拉塞爾斯家族===
拉塞爾斯家族在17世紀後期於[[西印度群島|西印度群島]]購買種植園。亨利·拉塞爾斯通過種植園產生的收入在1738年購買了莊園。他的兒子{{link-en|愛德溫·拉塞爾斯|Edwin Lascelles, 1st Baron Harewood}}是一位富裕的種植園主和奴隸主<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/abolition/building_britain_gallery_03.shtml|title=History - British History in depth: Slavery and the Building of Britain|publisher=BBC|access-date=2019-02-15|archive-date=2019-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216232224/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/abolition/building_britain_gallery_03.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在1759年至1771年修建了哈伍德宮<ref name="Jones">{{cite book|title=Architecture of England, Scotland, and Wales|last=Jones|first=Nigel R.|pages=133–135|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|year=2005|location=Westwood, CT, USA|isbn=0313318506}}</ref>，取代最初的建築。

愛德溫聘請北英格蘭建築家{{link-en|約翰·卡爾|John Carr (architect)}}設計新的建築，並於1759年動工，1765年大致完成。[[羅伯特·亞當|羅伯特·亞當]]則負責室內設計部分，並於1765年獲得批准。亞當也對卡爾設計的建築外側進行小幅改動，包括庭園景觀<ref name="Jones"/>。此後直到1840年代[[第三代哈伍德伯爵亨利·拉塞尔斯|第三代哈伍德伯爵亨利·拉塞尔斯]]聘請[[查爾斯·巴里|查爾斯·巴里]]改造建築之前，哈伍德宮幾乎沒有變動。巴里在每個侧翼增加了第二层，以提供新的臥室，並拆除了南門廊​​，修建了正式的花壇和露台<ref name="Jones"/>。

===20世紀===
1922年，{{link-en|亨利·拉塞爾斯,第六代哈伍德伯爵|Henry Lascelles, 6th Earl of Harewood|第六代哈伍德伯爵亨利·拉塞爾斯}}和[[喬治五世|喬治五世]]的獨生女[[瑪麗公主_(哈伍德伯爵夫人)|瑪麗公主]]結婚。兩人最初住在附近的{{link-en|戈爾茲伯勒廳|Goldsborough Hall}}，在1929年搬入哈伍德宮<ref name="Jones"/>。

第二次世界大戰期間，這座建築被用作療養院<ref>{{cite web |title=Leeds Legacies |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/legacies/work/england/leeds/gallery_6.shtml |publisher=BBC |access-date=2019-09-25 |quote=During World War II Harewood House was used as a resident convalescent hospital. |archive-date=2019-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925070737/http://www.bbc.co.uk/legacies/work/england/leeds/gallery_6.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但在1940年代後期，瑪麗公主和她的家人已經搬回哈伍德宮，但建築本身和花園仍然開放<ref>{{cite news |title=Harewood House open on Monday |url=https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood%20%20house%20%20gardens%20%20%20opened&county=yorkshire%2c%20england&from=1944&to=1949 |access-date=2019-09-25 |newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post |location=Yorkshire, England |date=1949-07-29 |quote=Harewood House open on Monday - HAREWOOD House and gardens will open to the public on Monday from 11 a.m. to... |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103550/https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood++house++gardens+++opened&county=yorkshire%2C+england&from=1944&to=1949 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並定期舉辦{{link-en|約克郡交響樂團|Yorkshire Symphony Orchestra}}的演奏會和{{link-en|利茲音樂節 (古典音樂)|Leeds Festival (classical music)|利茲音樂節}}等音樂活動。1965年，瑪麗公主在哈伍德宮突發心髒病<ref name="newton">{{cite news |last1=Newton |first1=Grace |title=The Queen's Lost Family: TV documentary tells the story of the royal letters found in a Yorkshire country house |url=https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/heritage-and-retro/heritage/queens-lost-family-tv-documentary-tells-story-royal-letters-found-yorkshire-country-house-1751595 |access-date=2020-06-14 |work=Yorkshire Post |date=2019-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614175314/https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/heritage-and-retro/heritage/queens-lost-family-tv-documentary-tells-story-royal-letters-found-yorkshire-country-house-1751595 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的長子{{link-en|喬治·拉塞爾斯,第七代哈伍德伯爵|George Lascelles, 7th Earl of Harewood|第七代哈伍德伯爵喬治·拉塞爾斯}}在1947年繼承了爵位，並居住在哈伍德<ref>{{cite news |title=Several well-known musical authorities from Leeds tell of the opportunities afforded them to talk things musical to her Royal Highness |url=https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood%20%20house%20%20musical%20%20festival%20%20triennial&county=yorkshire%2c%20england&from=1944&to=1949 |access-date=2019-09-25 |newspaper=Yorkshire Evening Post |location=Yorkshire, England |date=1949-01-10 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103554/https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood++house++musical++festival++triennial&county=yorkshire%2C+england&from=1944&to=1949 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Leeds Reception to Lord and Lady Harewood |url=https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=lord%20%20harewood%20%20%20yorkshire%20%20symphony%20%20orchestra&county=yorkshire%2c%20england&from=1944&to=1949 |access-date=2018-09-25 |newspaper=The Yorkshire Post / Yorkshire and Evening Post |location=Yorkshire, England |date=1949-11-23 |page=1 [Front page of The Yorkshire Post - 1949-11-23] |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103623/https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=lord++harewood+++yorkshire++symphony++orchestra&county=yorkshire%2C+england&from=1944&to=1949 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=B. |first1=E. |title=Significant Choice for Y.S.O. concert |url=https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000687/19500220/131/0006 |access-date=2019-04-11 |newspaper=Yorkshire Post and Leeds Intelligencer |date=1950-02-20 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103553/https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/account/register?countrykey=0&showgiftvoucherclaimingoptions=false&gift=false&nextpage=%2faccount%2flogin%3freturnurl%3d%252fviewer%252fbl%252f0000687%252f19500220%252f131%252f0006&rememberme=false&cookietracking=false&partnershipkey=0&newsletter=false&offers=false&registerreason=none&showsubscriptionoptions=false&showcouponmessaging=false&showfreetrialmessaging=false&showregisteroptions=false&showloginoptions=false&isonlyupgradeable=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Bradbury |url=https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood%20%20yorkshire%20%20symphony%20%20orchestr%20a&county=yorkshire%2C%20england&from=1940&to=1949&page=5 |work=Yorkshire Post and Leeds Intelligencer |location=Yorkshire, England |date=1949-03-21 |access-date=2018-11-24 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103555/https://www.genesreunited.co.uk/searchbna/results?memberlastsubclass=none&searchhistorykey=0&keywords=harewood++yorkshire++symphony++orchestr+a&county=yorkshire%2C+england&from=1940&to=1949&page=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Whitaker |first1=J. |title=An Almanack for the Year of Our Lord 1955, Volume 87 |date=1955 |publisher=J. Whitaker |page=1003 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FFMQAAAAIAAJ&q=Yorkshire+Symphony+Orchestra+Harewood+House&dq=Yorkshire+Symphony+Orchestra+Harewood+House |access-date=2019-10-08 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103550/https://books.google.com/books?id=FFMQAAAAIAAJ&q=Yorkshire+Symphony+Orchestra+Harewood+House&dq=Yorkshire+Symphony+Orchestra+Harewood+House |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1947年開始，莊園外側的{{link-en|多爾宮|Dower House}}被作為[[獨立學校|獨立學校]]校舍使用<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk/about-gateways/|title=About Gateways|publisher=Gateways School|access-date=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114143834/https://www.gatewaysschool.co.uk/about-gateways/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===21世紀===
拉塞爾斯家族和{{link-en|大衛·拉塞爾斯,第八代哈伍德伯爵|David Lascelles, 8th Earl of Harewood|第八代哈伍德伯爵大衛·拉塞爾斯}}現在仍然在這裡居住<ref name="Jones"/>。但建築和花園的所有權已轉移至哈伍德宮信託，並且在全年大部分時間對外開放。2009年，哈伍德宮贏得年度景點獎<ref name="hh2003">{{Cite web|url=http://www.harewood.org.uk/newsletter/newsletter4.pdf|title=Harewood Card Newsletter. Autumn/Winter 2003-04|publisher=Harewood.org|access-date=2007-09-28|archive-date=2007-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928142157/http://www.harewood.org.uk/newsletter/newsletter4.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

哈伍德宮收集了眾多義大利文藝復興時期的名家畫作，以及[[約書亞·雷諾茲|約書亞·雷諾茲]]、[[約翰·霍普納|約翰·霍普納]]、[[湯馬士·勞倫斯|湯馬士·勞倫斯]]的家族肖像畫，並定期在露台舉辦美術展。哈伍德宮內還有獲得米其林評分的餐廳<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/community/michelin-star-restaurant-moves-into-stately-home-to-offer-tasty-posh-nosh-1-4776971|title=Michelin star restaurant moves into stately home to offer tasty posh nosh|publisher=Yorkshire Evening Post|access-date=2012-07-31|archive-date=2012-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731052609/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/community/michelin-star-restaurant-moves-into-stately-home-to-offer-tasty-posh-nosh-1-4776971|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了建築之外，哈伍德宮還擁有面積達{{convert|100|acre}}的花園，包括喜馬拉雅花園和窣堵坡，一個教育用鳥園，一個遊樂場以及{{link-en|諸聖教堂 (哈伍德)|All Saints' Church, Harewood|諸聖教堂}}。2007年5月至2008年10月，約克郡第一座天文館{{link-en|約克郡天文館|Yorkshire Planetarium}}亦位於這裡<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/news/leeds-planetarium-a-meteoric-failure-1-2240476|title=Leeds planetarium - a meteoric failure|access-date=2018-03-31|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401005153/https://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/news/leeds-planetarium-a-meteoric-failure-1-2240476|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==流行文化==
哈伍德宮是1991年喜劇電影《{{link-en|英王拉爾夫|King Ralph}}》的拍攝地點<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.british-film-locations.com/King-Ralph-1991 |title=Where was ''King Ralph'' filmed? |publisher=British Film Locations |access-date=2017-10-31 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424141211/https://ir-uk.amazon-adsystem.com/e/ir?t=ukon0f-21&l=ur2&o=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1996年開始，部分莊園被用作[[獨立電視台_(英國)|ITV]]肥皂劇《[[愛默戴爾|愛默戴爾]]》的拍攝場地。電視劇《[[維多利亞_(電視劇)|維多利亞]]》亦在哈伍德宮拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068069/locations|title=Emmerdale (TV Series 1972– )|access-date=2018-12-31|via=www.imdb.com|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208103604/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068069/locations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年7月1日，愛爾蘭團體[[西城男孩|西城男孩]]在哈伍德宮舉辦演唱會。哈伍德宮也是電影《[[唐頓莊園_(電影)|唐頓莊園]]》的外景地<ref>{{cite web|title=Downton Abbey (2019) - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt6398184/locations|access-date=2020-10-07|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226053220/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6398184/locations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2018年播出的BBC聖誕節特別節目《{{link-en|瑪麗·貝里|Mary Berry}}的聖誕節鄉村別墅》節目在哈伍德宮拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0bwddm6|title=BBC Two - Mary Berry's Country House at Christmas|website=BBC|access-date=2018-12-31|archive-date=2019-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190101003455/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0bwddm6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

